le=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">表示連登 facebook 網絡廣泛地區已錄得或預料會有每秒三毛回覆量超過70次/禁70次正評的網絡分化攻勢，且攻勢可能持續或於今晚或明朝早上升級。</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNv7C24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNv7C24.jpg&h=73f7da13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">注意事項</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>網民應注意username 同 三毛開post 目的 而非三毛post正評數量。<br />\n網民應負皮三毛post 入去屌佢老母 而毋須參與分化討論。<br />\n鍵盤戰士應努力推正經post 例如準備時項去抵擋三毛攻勢。<br />\n三毛會開一啲反共post 減低大家戒心 請細心思考現時網絡上所有言論。<br />\n一般市民應少上連登 關電視 而休養等待明天遊行。<br />\n鬼得一隻 林奠 其他完全唔重要 。</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZB4gyv7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZB4gyv7.gif&h=7cacc0df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7dc8700d5efe251c53e72027c71b6d669d32a686","tid":1192844,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"fea856cc350eb658b8632ca9f14009f1fa6bf270","tid":1192844,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:36:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:37:37.000Z","msg":"冇計，佢哋得到大多數市民支持"},{"pid":"9820afd711c4fb1891db1de3e9d5804fa241e7a2","tid":1192844,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:37:47.000Z","msg":"6月9號遊行嘅方針:兄弟爬山，各自努力，避免割席，拒絕篤灰，不打飛機，不傳耳語，不搞抹黑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1192414\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1192414</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3f1f80340e6ef8ddd11bc576d032e4a34599c004","tid":1192844,"uid":52230,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:40:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>槍口一致對外！<br />\n<br />\n不要分化！不要懷疑隊友！<br />\n<br />\n有人被捕立即群擁而上集體救援！<br />\n<br />\n勿比機會警犬單獨拉走同伴！<br />\n<br />\n一切行動必須群體出發！ <br />\n<br />\nStick Together Team! 不要落單！<br